      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hey, I'm working on a paper for my psych history class about the eugenics movement in the early 1900s. Can you help me out by elaborating on the specific arguments and 'scientific' justifications that eugenicists used back then to try and prove there were different racial hierarchies? I need to understand their logic for my analysis.",
